<text><body>
<lb n="1383b07"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="1383b08"/><head type="no">No. 2882</head>
<lb n="1383b09"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="1"/><jhead><note n="1383014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】大英博物館藏燉煌本, S. 418, 【甲】大英博物館藏燉煌本, S2&unrec;17, 甲本首缺</note>佛說&CB00057;魅經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="1383b10"/>
<lb n="1383b11"/><div1 type="jing"><p>爾時佛在舍衛國妙龍□□□□□□□切眾
<lb n="1383b12"/>生作罪不可論盡□□□□□□□道令得開
<lb n="1383b13"/>悟。吾<note n="1383015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以上甲本缺</note>今為汝說過去未來之見。往昔空王
<lb n="1383b14"/>佛時。給孤獨園中有一老狐。穴前燒其脂火。
<lb n="1383b15"/>夜半日月五星下造作魅蠱。上牽天神<note n="1383016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔下牽〕－【甲】</note><app n="1383016"><lem>下牽</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="1383b16"/>五帝。復牽山神復牽河伯將軍。復牽五道大
<lb n="1383b17"/>神。呼取百鬼造作魅蠱。或作蒲人。或作人形
<lb n="1383b18"/>像。或作符書厭禱&CB00057;詛。或取人姓字。或取棘
<lb n="1383b19"/>針。或<note n="1383017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">果＝裹【甲】</note><app n="1383017"><lem>果</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">裹</rdg></app>黃土。或向日月獨語不自覺知。或
<lb n="1383b20"/>取人家衣裳。或取人衣帶。或取五綵綖縷。或
<lb n="1383b21"/>取人家甑帶。或取人家&CB00140;&CB00096;瓦器。或取人家
<lb n="1383b22"/><note n="1383018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔驢馬牛羊〕－【甲】</note><app n="1383018"><lem>驢馬牛羊</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="1383019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00337;＋（羊雞）【甲】</note><app n="1383019"><lem>&CB00337;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00337;羊雞</rdg></app>狗毛。或取人家五<note n="1383020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">行作具＝形之事【甲】</note><app n="1383020"><lem>行作具</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">形之事</rdg></app>。或
<lb n="1383b23"/>取人家門<note n="1383021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">楔＝簟【甲】</note><app n="1383021"><lem>楔</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">簟</rdg></app>。或取人家匙箸作魅蠱。或<note n="1383022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">奇＝騎【甲】</note><app n="1383022"><lem>奇</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">騎</rdg></app>
<lb n="1383b24"/>麻鄒馬。或刺人身。或<note n="1383023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">刺＝針【甲】</note><app n="1383023"><lem>刺</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">針</rdg></app>人心<note n="1383024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔胎〕－【甲】</note><app n="1383024"><lem>胎</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。或<note n="1383025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">計＝針【甲】</note><app n="1383025"><lem>計</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">針</rdg></app>人
<lb n="1383b25"/>手&CB00560;。或針<note n="1383026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔人〕－【甲】＊</note><app n="1383026"><lem>人</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>眼孔。或針<anchor id="fxT85p1383b01"/>人腰背。或取人
<lb n="1383b26"/>頭毛。或取黃土。或取五綵帛。或取人上下衣
<lb n="1383b27"/>帶。或魅蠱人田<note n="1383027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">苗＝作【甲】</note><app n="1383027"><lem>苗</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">作</rdg></app>。或捉群抄舉向壁獨語。
<lb n="1383b28"/>或作狩形像。或作人頭形像。或作<note n="1383028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔魅等〕－【甲】</note><app n="1383028"><lem>魅等</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>符
<lb n="1383b29"/>書厭禱&CB00057;咀。或<note n="1383029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔令〕－【甲】</note><app n="1383029"><lem>令</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>作人形言說不以道理。
<lb n="1383b30"/><note n="1383030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">或＋（作）【甲】</note><app n="1383030"><lem>或</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">或作</rdg></app>魅蠱<note n="1383031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">人＋（田或魅蠱人）【甲】</note><app n="1383031"><lem>人</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">人田或魅蠱人</rdg></app>家牛<note n="1383032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">馬羊犬＝羊犬馬【甲】</note><app n="1383032"><lem>馬羊犬</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">羊犬馬</rdg></app><note n="1383033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔雞&CB00337;狗〕－【甲】</note><app n="1383033"><lem>雞&CB00337;狗</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。或作生
<pb ed="T" id="T85.2882.1383c" n="1383c"/>
<lb n="1383c01"/>人口舌。或作馬形。或作鬼神形。或作牛羊
<lb n="1383c02"/><note n="1383034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔&CB00337;狗〕－【甲】</note><app n="1383034"><lem>&CB00337;狗</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>形。造<note n="1383035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">魅之＝作魅【甲】</note><app n="1383035"><lem>魅之</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">作魅</rdg></app>人。生死無道。強殺良善。
<lb n="1383c03"/><note n="1383036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">若＋（自作若）【甲】</note><app n="1383036"><lem>若</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">若自作若</rdg></app>教他作。千殃萬罪。造者自當三梁六柱。
<lb n="1383c04"/>還著本主。萬罪殃還自滅亡。急去三千六百
<lb n="1383c05"/><note n="1383037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一十〕－【甲】</note><app n="1383037"><lem>一十</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>里。止不得久停。今請東方青帝神王來
<lb n="1383c06"/>食魅人腹。<note n="1383038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（今請西方…頭）十三字∞（今請南方…眼）十三字【甲】</note><note n="1383038" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="a"/>（今請西方…頭）十三字∞（今請南方…眼）十三字【甲】</note>今請<note n="1383039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔西方…請〕十三字－【甲】</note><note n="1383039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔西方…頭〕－【甲】</note><app n="1383039" word-count="11"><lem>西方白帝神王來食魅人
<lb n="1383c07"/>頭</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。<note n="1383040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（今請西方…頭）十三字∞（今請南方…眼）十三字【甲】</note><note n="1383040" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="i"/>〔今請〕－【甲】，（今請西方…頭）十三字∞（今請南方…眼）十三字【甲】</note><app n="1383040"><lem>今請</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>南方赤帝神王來食魅人<note n="1383041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">眼＝腸【甲】</note><app n="1383041"><lem>眼</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">腸</rdg></app>。今請
<lb n="1383c08"/>北方黑帝神王來食<note n="1383042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">魅＝媚【甲】</note><app n="1383042"><lem>魅</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">媚</rdg></app>人<note n="1383043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00560;＝眼【甲】</note><app n="1383043"><lem>&CB00560;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">眼</rdg></app>。今請中央<note n="1383044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">皇＝黃【甲】</note><app n="1383044"><lem>皇</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">黃</rdg></app>
<lb n="1383c09"/>帝神王來食魅人手。爾時眾中有一菩薩。名
<lb n="1383c10"/>為大力。<note n="1383045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">整衣＝自正衣服【甲】</note><app n="1383045"><lem>整衣</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">自正衣服</rdg></app>為佛作禮白佛言。世尊弟子不
<lb n="1383c11"/>解罪福。見世間眾生。多有五逆不信首道。共
<lb n="1383c12"/>相<note n="1383046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">魚肉有＝漁食【甲】</note><app n="1383046"><lem>魚肉有</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">漁食</rdg></app><note n="1383047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">常＋（有）【甲】</note><app n="1383047"><lem>常</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">常有</rdg></app>惡念。不知生天堂受樂。不知
<lb n="1383c13"/>有地獄憂苦。共相煎煮魅<note n="1383048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蠱＝故【甲】</note><app n="1383048"><lem>蠱</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">故</rdg></app>良善。唯願世
<lb n="1383c14"/>尊。乃為弟子分別解說。令得道&CB00528;度脫一切
<lb n="1383c15"/>爾時佛告大力菩薩。汝今<note n="1383049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">未＝得開【甲】</note><app n="1383049"><lem>未</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">得開</rdg></app>解。<note n="1383050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吾＋（今）【甲】</note><app n="1383050"><lem>吾</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">吾今</rdg></app>為汝<note n="1383051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔等〕－【甲】</note><app n="1383051"><lem>等</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="1383c16"/>分別解說。<note n="1383052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">汝今諦聽＝爾時佛言【甲】</note><app n="1383052"><lem>汝今諦聽</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">爾時佛言</rdg></app>。吾遣四天王等<note n="1383053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">令＝今【甲】</note><app n="1383053"><lem>令</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">今</rdg></app>下
<lb n="1383c17"/>世間。療治百惡不得停止。急去千里可得免
<lb n="1383c18"/>脫。&CB00057;曰。魅公字槃<note n="1383054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">永＝市【甲】</note><app n="1383054"><lem>永</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">市</rdg></app>都魅母字槃石奴。今
<lb n="1383c19"/>知汝姓字知汝姓名。若作魅蠱<note n="1383055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔者〕－【甲】</note><app n="1383055"><lem>者</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>返受其殃。
<lb n="1383c20"/>汝教他作身自滅亡。吾今請四天神王<note n="1383056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔來〕－【甲】</note><app n="1383056"><lem>來</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>錄
<lb n="1383c21"/>魅<note n="1383057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔人〕－【甲】</note><app n="1383057"><lem>人</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>名字。吾今&CB00057;魅人頭破作七分如<note n="1383058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">阿梨樹＝阿犁樹【甲】下同</note><app n="1383058"><lem>阿
<lb n="1383c22"/>梨樹</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">阿犁樹</rdg></app>枝。今當知汝姓名急去他方不得停止。
<lb n="1383c23"/>今當請南無佛陀來&CB00057;魅人頭破作七分如阿
<lb n="1383c24"/>梨樹枝。今當請四天<note n="1383059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（大）＋龍【甲】</note><app n="1383059"><lem>龍</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">大龍</rdg></app>王來&CB00057;魅人頭破作
<lb n="1383c25"/>七分如阿梨樹枝。今當<note n="1383060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">請＋（牛頭）【甲】</note><app n="1383060"><lem>請</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">請牛頭</rdg></app>阿傍來&CB00057;魅<note n="1383061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">人＋（不得停止）【甲】</note><app n="1383061"><lem>人</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">人不得停止</rdg></app>
<lb n="1383c26"/>頭破作七分如阿梨樹枝。<note n="1383062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔不得…枝〕二十四字－【甲】</note><app n="1383062" word-count="24"><lem>不得停止。佛有如
<pb ed="T" id="T85.2882.1384a" n="1384a"/>
<lb n="1384a01"/>是大神&CB00057;。此魅人頭破作七分如阿梨樹枝</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。
<lb n="1384a02"/>今當請普賢菩薩來&CB00057;魅人頭破作七分如阿
<lb n="1384a03"/>梨樹枝。今當請<note n="1384001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔大智…請〕四十二字－【甲】</note><app n="1384001" word-count="42"><lem>大智菩薩來&CB00057;魅人頭破作
<lb n="1384a04"/>七分如阿梨樹枝。今當請更明菩薩來&CB00057;魅人
<lb n="1384a05"/>頭破作七分如阿梨樹枝。今當請</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>月光菩薩
<lb n="1384a06"/>來&CB00057;魅人頭破作七分如阿梨樹枝。今當請
<lb n="1384a07"/>蒙光菩薩來&CB00057;魅人頭破作七分如阿梨樹
<lb n="1384a08"/>枝。今當請火光菩薩來&CB00057;魅人頭破作七分
<lb n="1384a09"/>如阿梨樹枝。今當請華光菩薩來&CB00057;魅人頭
<lb n="1384a10"/>破作七分如阿梨樹枝。今當請月明菩薩來
<lb n="1384a11"/>&CB00057;魅人頭破作七分如阿梨樹枝。今當請文
<lb n="1384a12"/>光菩薩來&CB00057;魅人頭破作七分如阿梨樹枝。
<lb n="1384a13"/>今當請龍光菩薩來&CB00057;魅人頭破作七分如阿
<lb n="1384a14"/>梨樹枝。今當請明星菩薩來&CB00057;魅人頭破作
<lb n="1384a15"/>七分如阿梨樹枝。今當請千陽菩薩來&CB00057;魅
<lb n="1384a16"/>人頭破作七分如阿梨樹<note n="1384002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">枝＋（今當請勇力菩薩來&CB00057;魅人頭破作七分如阿犁樹枝）【甲】</note><app n="1384002"><lem>枝</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">枝今當請勇力菩薩來&CB00057;魅人頭破作七分如阿犁樹枝</rdg></app>。今當請普明菩
<lb n="1384a17"/>薩來&CB00057;魅人頭破作七分如阿梨樹枝。今當
<lb n="1384a18"/>請大明菩薩來&CB00057;魅人頭破作七分如阿梨樹
<lb n="1384a19"/><note n="1384003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">枝＋（今當請轉輪菩薩來&CB00057;魅人頭破作七分如阿犁樹枝）【甲】</note><app n="1384003"><lem>枝</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">枝今當請轉輪菩薩來&CB00057;魅人頭破作七分如阿犁樹枝</rdg></app>。今當請同光菩薩來&CB00057;魅人頭破作七分
<lb n="1384a20"/>如阿梨樹枝。<note n="1384004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔今當…枝〕二十一字－【甲】</note><app n="1384004" word-count="21"><lem>今當請日中菩薩來&CB00057;魅人頭
<lb n="1384a21"/>破作七分如阿梨樹枝</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。今當請建立菩薩來
<lb n="1384a22"/>&CB00057;魅人頭破作七分如阿梨樹枝。今當請樹
<lb n="1384a23"/>王菩薩來&CB00057;魅人頭破作七分如阿梨樹枝。
<lb n="1384a24"/>今當請龍<note n="1384005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天＝王【甲】</note><app n="1384005"><lem>天</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">王</rdg></app>菩薩來&CB00057;魅人頭破作七分如
<lb n="1384a25"/>阿梨樹枝。今當請地動菩薩來&CB00057;魅人頭破
<lb n="1384a26"/>作七分如阿梨樹枝。今當請東方青帝神王
<lb n="1384a27"/>來&CB00057;魅人不得停止。今當請南方赤帝神王
<lb n="1384a28"/>來&CB00057;魅人不得停止。今當請西方白帝神王
<lb n="1384a29"/>來&CB00057;魅人不得停止。今當請北方黑帝神王
<pb ed="T" id="T85.2882.1384b" n="1384b"/>
<lb n="1384b01"/>來&CB00057;魅人不得停止。今當呼日月五星二十
<lb n="1384b02"/>八宿來攝魅人不得停止。急去千里。東方大
<lb n="1384b03"/><note n="1384006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">狩＝獸【甲】</note><app n="1384006"><lem>狩</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">獸</rdg></app>來食魅人身。南方蜈蚣來食魅人<note n="1384007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔眼西…人〕九字－【甲】</note><app n="1384007" word-count="9"><lem>眼西
<lb n="1384b04"/>方白象來食魅人</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>頭。北方黑象來<note n="1384008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">啄＝食【甲】</note><app n="1384008"><lem>啄</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">食</rdg></app>魅人心
<lb n="1384b05"/>藏。中央黃帝<note n="1384009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔神〕－【甲】</note><app n="1384009"><lem>神</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>龍王來食魅人神。吾見魅
<lb n="1384b06"/>人眼目角張。或作猖狂不似人形。或在人門
<lb n="1384b07"/>前。或<note n="1384010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">在＋（人）【甲】</note><app n="1384010"><lem>在</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">在人</rdg></app>屋&M034294;。或在碓磨上。或在人田地間
<lb n="1384b08"/>跳<note n="1384011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">良＝踉【甲】</note><app n="1384011"><lem>良</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">踉</rdg></app>不止。或正月歲日。或正月十五日。或
<lb n="1384b09"/>時<note n="1384012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">節＋（之）【甲】</note><app n="1384012"><lem>節</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">節之</rdg></app>日。或燒其脂火&CB00057;說不止。吾知汝<note n="1384013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">姓＋（字知汝姓）【甲】</note><app n="1384013"><lem>姓</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">姓字知汝姓</rdg></app>
<lb n="1384b10"/>名不得停止急去他方。若坐<note n="1384014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">滅亡若立＝坐喪若立倒地【甲】</note><app n="1384014"><lem>滅亡若立</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">坐喪若立倒地</rdg></app>消滅。
<lb n="1384b11"/>頭破作七分如阿梨樹枝。若生<note n="1384015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">赤＝人【甲】</note><app n="1384015"><lem>赤</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">人</rdg></app>口<note n="1384016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔赤〕－【甲】</note><app n="1384016"><lem>赤</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>舌
<lb n="1384b12"/>菩薩&CB00057;令消滅急去不得<note n="1384017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">久＝停【甲】</note><app n="1384017"><lem>久</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">停</rdg></app>留。爾時世尊
<lb n="1384b13"/><note n="1384018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（唱）＋言【甲】</note><app n="1384018"><lem>言</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">唱言</rdg></app>。我今告十方眾生等。吾<note n="1384019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">今為＝語【甲】</note><app n="1384019"><lem>今為</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">語</rdg></app>汝一切眾
<lb n="1384b14"/>生<note n="1384020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（為）＋善【甲】</note><app n="1384020"><lem>善</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">為善</rdg></app>男子善女人<note n="1384021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">說此＝等造作【甲】</note><app n="1384021"><lem>說此</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">等造作</rdg></app>&CB00057;魅經。時有十方諸
<lb n="1384b15"/>佛過去七佛。十六王子佛。天上諸菩薩天人
<lb n="1384b16"/>羅漢。四天大王天龍八部。諸善<note n="1384022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（鬼）＋神【甲】</note><app n="1384022"><lem>神</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">鬼神</rdg></app>四道果
<lb n="1384b17"/>人。一會<note n="1384023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔在〕－【甲】</note><app n="1384023"><lem>在</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>須彌山頭龍華樹下。<note n="1384024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">平＝許【甲】</note><app n="1384024"><lem>平</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">許</rdg></app>量眾生
<lb n="1384b18"/>云何可度。若有比丘比丘尼優婆塞優婆夷
<lb n="1384b19"/>男子女人。有能燒香禮佛受持此經供養不
<lb n="1384b20"/>絕令人得福。若有憂苦之人能生善念皆得
<lb n="1384b21"/>天堂之樂。若有人轉此經時。先清潔身行道
<lb n="1384b22"/>燒香受持可得度脫。若能誦此經七遍。&CB00057;魅
<lb n="1384b23"/>頭破作七分如阿梨樹枝。<note n="1384025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（一切…會））十二字＝（（佛說此經已））五字【甲】</note><app n="1384025" word-count="12"><lem>一切眾苦皆悉解
<lb n="1384b24"/>脫。爾時一會</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">佛說此經已</rdg></app>一切眾<note n="1384026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">生＝會【甲】</note><app n="1384026"><lem>生</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">會</rdg></app>。聞經歡<note n="1384027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">仰為佛＝喜【甲】</note><app n="1384027"><lem>仰為佛</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">喜</rdg></app>作
<lb n="1384b25"/>禮<note n="1384028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔持念〕－【甲】</note><app n="1384028"><lem>持念</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>奉行</p>
<lb n="1384b26"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead><note n="1384029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（佛說）＋&CB00057;【甲】</note><app n="1384029"><lem>&CB00057;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">佛說&CB00057;</rdg></app>魅<note n="1384030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＋（一卷）【甲】，此下甲本奧書曰令願進子一心供養</note><app n="1384030"><lem>經</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">經一卷</rdg></app><note n="1384030" place="foot" type="rest">此下甲本奧書曰令願進子一心供養</note></jhead></juan></div1>
